description:
Nana is a homonculus based on http://anidb.net/ch93242 [Mia] that was with the Iron Golem in the center room of the maze created by http://anidb.net/ch96007 [Trazayuya]. http://anidb.net/ch91583 [Satou] became her master after he defeated her previous master, http://anidb.net/ch96005 [Zen].
Source: Death March Wikia
